-- Dick's Sporting Goods gets acquisition clearance
-- 
-- Fri Dec 22, 2006 4:45pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/12/22/us-dickssportinggoods-acquisition-idUSWEN158320061222

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - Sporting goods retailer Dick's Sporting Goods Inc. ( DKS.N ) said on Friday it received early termination of the waiting period under the Hart-Scott-Rodino antitrust law for its pending acquisition of Golf Galaxy Inc. GCXY.O 

 Dick's Sporting Goods is acquiring Golf Galaxy for about $225 million in cash to strengthen its position in the golf equipment and apparel market. The deal needs approval by Golf Galaxy shareholders.